m_q.target_metric: Chi-square statistic and p-value for independence test between geographical region and fire causes for January-March fires with known causes
sub_questions: Breakdown of fire causes by geographical region for January-March fires
Chi-square test of independence between region and cause
Report chi-square statistic and p-value as list of two numbers

schema_conflicts: Variable description file has different structure than main data file

scale_issues: cause_ind appears to be numeric encoding of cause

format_notes: cause codes: U=unknown, N=natural, H=human, L=lightning, O=other

constraints: Only fires starting in January, February, or March
derived_filters: Filter cause column for non-'U' values
statistical_tests: Chi-square test of independence between region and cause categories
output_format_requirements: List of two numbers: [chi-square statistic, p-value]
